# Fitness Tracker Web App

A full-featured fitness tracking web application built with
Firebase Authentication, Firestore, and Firebase Hosting.

## Live Demo
https://litnessfitness-72cb2.web.app/index.html

## Features
- User authentication (sign up, login, email verification)
- Workout tracking with sets & PR detection
- Exercise selector with categories
- Progress charts (strength & body groups)
- Persistent local + cloud data
- Premium UI/UX with animations

## Tech Stack
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Firebase Auth
- Firestore
- Firebase Hosting
- Chart.js

## Setup (Local)
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Adam Dimkovski/FitnessWebsite.git
cd FitnessWebsite
firebase serve
